caption.p: a) Voltammogram regions enclosing the oxidation peak of selected background subtracted voltammograms taken from the data set of Fig 5, superimposed with asterisks showing the curvature boundaries for each voltammogram. Stimulation parameters for the traces X,Y, and Z are as follows X: 0.14mA, 1.46ms pulse width, 180 pulses, 90Hz Y: 0.16mA, 1.57ms pulse width, 180 pulses, 90Hz Z: 0.15mA, 1.45ms pulse width, 180 pulses, 90Hz (b) Oxidation charges corresponding to the data set of Fig 5, obtained with curvature limits, plotted as function of the duty cycle for the 90 Hz, two-second stimulations.
